The '''Rings of Power''' can refer to:

* The '''[[Rings of Power]]''', twenty [[Magic]] rings that were created by the [[Gwaith-i-Mírdain]] and [[Sauron|Annatar]].

* '''''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power]]''''', the television adaptation set in the [[Second Age]], produced by [[Amazon Studios]].
